: desc = \"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"\"\",出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-12T01:10:18Z to 2025-06-12T01:29:18Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 01:10:18+00:00 to 2025-06-12 01:29:18+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "raw_log_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载日志数据。UUID: 1193b5d8-230，共 2 条错误日志", "filtered_logs": "node_name,service_name,pod_name,message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"96cbb0a2-166a-4005-9678-b226365b4e74\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"eca392c1-8edc-43f2-ae42-297267cef484\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-12T01:10:23.761071627Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"24687d5c-273d-4bc1-83ee-12c1adf013c8\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"2168771e-7ecd-449a-b701-75c8983a1f35\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-12T01:10:37.853341872Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-1"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-12T01:10:18Z to 2025-06-12T01:29:18Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 01:10:18+00:00 to 2025-06-12 01:29:18+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我来分析验证cartservice是否为根因的假设。\n\n从日志数据可以看到，在故障时间段内，有两个frontend服务实例都报告了相同的错误：\n- frontend-0 (节点aiops-k8s-03)\n- frontend-1 (节点aiops-k8s-07)\n\n错误信息明确显示：`connection error: desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"`\n\n**分析结果**：\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：日志中明确出现了\"connection refused\"错误，这是典型的端口连接拒绝问题\n2. **目标服务确认**：错误指向cartservice的7070端口（IP: 10.233.46.196:7070）\n3. **故障模式匹配**：这符合Port Misconfiguration故障模式的特征\n\n根据特殊故障模式识别规则：\n- 特征：日志含 `connection refused` + 目标服务健康但无法连接\n- detected_log_keys需要添加：`port`\n- component应为被调方服务：`cartservice`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"port\", \"connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"端口配置错误导致连接拒绝(port connection refused)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**：日志数据强烈支持cartservice是根因的假设。多个frontend实例都报告了连接cartservice时出现端口连接拒绝错误，这符合Port Misconfiguration故障模式，表明cartservice可能存在端口配置问题或服务不可用。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的Trace指标数据，我来分析\"cartservice是根因\"的假设是否成立。\n\n从指标数据可以看出：\n\n**支持cartservice是根因的证据：**\n1. **cartservice-1响应时间异常飙升**：`rrt_max`变化率174.61%（从5231.5到77184.0），`rrt`变化率131.38%\n2. **cartservice-1错误率显著升高**：`error_ratio` P99达到22.46%，`client_error_ratio` P99达到20.73%\n3. **cartservice表现最差**：相比其他服务，cartservice-1的响应时间恶化程度最为严重\n\n**需要注意的其他异常：**\n1. **节点内存使用率异常**：`aiops-k8s-04`节点的`node_memory_usage_rate`从29.64%上升到48.15%，变化率47.59%\n2. **多个服务响应时间异常**：recommendationservice-2、productcatalogservice-2等服务的`rrt_max`也有显著恶化\n\n**关键分析：**\n- cartservice-1位于`aiops-k8s-05`节点，而内存异常的是`aiops-k8s-04`节点，两者无直接关联\n- cartservice-1的响应时间和错误率异常是最直接的故障表现\n- 连接拒绝错误（connection refused）通常与服务不可用相关，与cartservice的响应时间异常和错误率升高相符\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice-1出现严重的响应时间异常（rrt_max变化率174.61%）和错误率升高（error_ratio P99达到22.46%），表明服务不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从5231.5上升到77184.0，rrt从1726.12上升到8335.63，error_ratio P99达到22.46%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取的trace数据分析，我现在可以验证\"cartservice是根因\"的假设。让我详细分析trace数据：\n\n## 分析结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"rrt_max\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个调用方（frontend-0, checkoutservice-0, checkoutservice-2）连接cartservice时出现'connection refused'错误，目标IP: 10.233.46.196:7070，表明cartservice服务不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用延迟异常飙升：AddItem操作从3583ms增至46407ms（延迟倍数12.9倍），GetCart操作从2314ms增至17308ms（延迟倍数7.5倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2调用redis的HMSET操作从1361ms增至29530ms（延迟倍数21.7倍），表明cartservice依赖的redis也存在性能问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现\n\n**支持cartservice是根因的证据：**\n\n1. **明确的连接拒绝错误**：多个调用方（frontend、checkoutservice）连接cartservice时出现\"connection refused\"错误，目标地址为10.233.46.196:7070，这是cartservice不可用的直接证据。\n\n2. **显著的延迟异常**：\n   - cartservice的AddItem操作延迟增加12.9倍\n   - GetCart操作延迟增加7.5倍\n   - 表明cartservice处理能力严重下降\n\n3. **错误传播路径**：\n   - frontend → cartservice (连接拒绝)\n   - checkoutservice → cartservice (连接拒绝)\n   - cartservice → redis (严重延迟)\n\n4. **根因定位**：cartservice是最下游出现问题的服务，其不可用导致上游服务（frontend、checkoutservice）出现连锁故障。\n\n**结论**：trace数据强烈支持\"cartservice是根因\"的假设，cartservice的服务不可用和性能严重下降是本次故障的根本原因。"}
